import React from "react"
import MemoizedMusicPlayer from "./musicPlayer.jsx"
import NavBar from "../components/Navbar.jsx"

function App() {
	return (
		<Router>
			<NavBar />
			<Routes>
				<Route path="/" element={<MemoizedMusicPlayer />} />
			</Routes>
		</Router>
	)
}

export default App
